WEBVTT

00:07.000 --> 00:09.029
Previously on "The Purge"...

00:09.030 --> 00:10.197
Long time no see.

00:10.198 --> 00:11.979
The hell, Ryan? You called her?

00:11.980 --> 00:12.991
I'm your savior here.

00:12.992 --> 00:14.809
You cut me into whatever
you're planning.

00:14.810 --> 00:16.203
Your husband and I had a deal.

00:16.204 --> 00:19.249
They got us the name of the
person who tried to Purge me.

00:19.250 --> 00:21.660
- Sam Tucker.
- We had an affair.

00:22.752 --> 00:24.502
So you think someone did this to her.

00:24.503 --> 00:27.609
We have cameras. They
might've caught something.

00:27.610 --> 00:28.619
